Q.4) Write a query that totals the orders for each day and places the results in 
descending order.
Ans--->

mysql> select count(odate), odate from orders
    -> group by odate
    -> order by odate desc;
+--------------+------------+
| count(odate) | odate      |
+--------------+------------+
|            2 | 1990-10-06 |
|            1 | 1990-10-05 |
|            2 | 1990-10-04 |
|            4 | 1990-10-03 |
+--------------+------------+
